Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.56,Sign06C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Castle Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.29,0:00:05.82,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I was so concerned about the start of school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.82,0:00:07.48,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,but two weeks have already passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:10.99,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:15.41,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Roromiya's roasting dried seaweed \Non the alcohol lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:17.32,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:20.29,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Roromiya brought a dog to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:21.62,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:24.20,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Roromiya is staring off into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:25.21,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:27.39,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Roromiya ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.19,0:00:38.50,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I should be more worried \Nabout her than myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.21,0:02:17.92,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,So if you apply this number here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:19.13,Title1E6,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(671,180)}Don't Think
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:19.89,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:22.07,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,And if you plug in this number here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:28.49,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.49,0:02:30.76,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing? \NHurry and take your seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.47,0:02:38.84,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:42.04,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,She vanished, right in the middle of P.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.04,0:02:45.23,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she just disappeared \Nduring the marathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:59.13,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's like you can never \Nguess what she's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:00.56,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,She's really cute but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:02.02,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:03.25,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:05.99,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.49,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm twice as bad, so why aren't \Nyou talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.93,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Watanuki, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.95,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:14.79,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,And now she just starts eating lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.33,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,She's unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:29.43,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.12,Default,Lunch lady,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.44,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:50.62,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Then you were quite foolish to \Neat your lunch early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:53.92,Sign06A,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Red Bean Bun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:55.99,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:58.74,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,My stomach doesn't feel so great right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:03.88,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:07.14,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like, I have some soy milk, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.23,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:20.82,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,I've thought you were nice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.65,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,ever since I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:25.07,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,She just said she loves me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:27.35,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.28,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're just saying that \Nbecause I gave you some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:30.74,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:32.91,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,My sixth sense told me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.36,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:38.12,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe my five senses?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:40.38,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're just making this up as you go along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:42.51,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:45.93,Inuboku-flashback,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,You really should interact \Nmore with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:52.56,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know how I'm supposed to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:58.89,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:01.84,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,But why are they rabbit ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:02.99,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Rabbit ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:05.75,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Because life is just one big game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.66,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:12.90,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a mysterious sprite, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.36,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:16.39,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't seen you since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.43,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:21.37,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,I can't reveal the nature of our relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:23.62,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds shady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:24.92,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.21,0:05:26.36,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:30.94,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,All I ever try to do is enjoy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:32.08,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,That's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:33.14,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He's so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:34.26,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:34.89,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:37.84,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Chiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.36,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He was funny, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.36,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:43.57,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,A white silk base, with an elaborate \Nand intricate lace trim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.17,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,All rounded up with a ribbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:46.86,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,How—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:50.88,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,What I love about lace is how \Nit really is an art form...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:53.04,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:56.51,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,It appears Watanuki got into a fight, \Nand he's in the nurse's office now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:57.71,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Could you show me where that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.00,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why didn't you say that \Nin the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.22,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,You're all torn up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.25,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.76,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,A delinquent's bruises are his medals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.25,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have a monopoly \Non that distinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:11.60,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.10,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.55,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,do you know when Watanuki stopped \Nwearing tighty-whities?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:20.27,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,It actually wasn't that long...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.27,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:26.61,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,They were calling Karuta weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:34.01,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she walks around in her \Nown world, but so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.45,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's still aware of what's \Ngoing on around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:40.54,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't just thinking... \NIt's something deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:44.38,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,She probably knows \Ninstinctively what's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:48.33,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. She's like a jungle hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.33,0:06:50.32,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,She's like Tarzan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.61,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:55.76,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Watanuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:57.89,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:01.02,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we leave them alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:02.72,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.57,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:16.88,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,They're really good friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:18.79,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they've known each \Nother since childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:22.87,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,More than friends, but not quite lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:25.67,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,A truly beautiful tale...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.96,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't invade people's privacy that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.39,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time, in a land far, far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:33.25,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,some people mingled with \Nsupernatural creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:37.71,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,The families descended from them \Nwere mysteriously prosperous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:39.49,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Among them were some individuals \Nin whom the blood of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:41.81,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,the creatures ran particularly strong. \NThey are known as throwbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.69,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,And that's who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:48.64,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,We were born on the exact day, \Nat the exact same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:50.79,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,and with the exact same \Npersonalities as our ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:52.53,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we've also inherited
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:53.99,Sign06B1,Text,0000,0000,0000,,The Fate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.95,Sign06B2,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Ancestor
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:56.40,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,their memories, and are mysteriously \Nbound to their same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.64,Sign06B3,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Throwback
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:59.45,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,These children were regarded as \Nthe second coming of the ancestors,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:02.73,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,and were raised by the whole house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.71,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,That is to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:08.20,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,essentially, the parents did not \Nfactor into their upbringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:10.18,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,The parents were just a womb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.17,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Having never experienced \Nthe concept of family,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:17.54,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,it's natural that we should be lonely. \NWaa! Waa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:20.02,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why remind me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:25.23,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Because the story is about two people \Nneeding each other and becoming close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.57,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if they're good or bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.23,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,You need relationships with \Nothers to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:31.25,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,That means you, too, Chiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:34.22,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Let's communicate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:40.41,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You really are meddlesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:46.53,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complicate it like, "I don't know \Nhow to interact with others."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:48.59,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.13,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wha— You looked into me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.85,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Watanuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.77,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:30.96,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Just one moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:34.63,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before, you don't \Nhave to do this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.90,Inuboku-flashback,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kagerou Shoukiin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:54.62,Inuboku-flashback,Kagerou,0000,0000,0000,,I am Soushi's old master and \NRirichiyo Shirakiin's fiancé!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:02.37,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He said that Miketsukami \Nused to serve him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:04.50,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.02,0:10:08.79,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,does that mean he knew I had a fiancé?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.60,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Roromiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:24.98,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,This, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:27.74,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,This, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:30.64,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,This, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.35,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,This, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:36.28,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.28,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,These are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:44.10,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That was unnecessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.73,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess I'll thank you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:50.75,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,However, this might give me a cavity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.04,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You should watch out, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:59.55,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,After I said that, she brought me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:01.97,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:08.09,Inuboku-flashback,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complicate it like, "I don't know \Nhow to interact with others."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:10.14,Inuboku-flashback,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:36.50,Sign06C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Castle Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:40.09,Sign06A,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Home Economics
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:41.94,Default,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to split into groups \Nand get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:45.54,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:48.35,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,To think that I'd have to be on your team...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:53.06,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Working in a group...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:56.11,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I need to be sure not to \Nalienate my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:01.98,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roromiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:05.66,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I have to keep an eye out, \Nand cover for her, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:13.65,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,15 grams of garam masala...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.73,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,10 grams of coriander.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.73,0:12:18.54,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That was 0.2 grams too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:19.63,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.09,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She criticized me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:25.66,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,There is no manual for cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:28.09,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Today's spices aren't fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.63,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,They've lost some flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:33.27,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,We must consider various factors, \Nand then improvise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:38.48,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking is about seeing the \Npossibilities clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:50.54,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The color of her eyes has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.67,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:07.40,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking is about seeing the \Npossibilities clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.43,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she said it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:11.78,Default,Background,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:36.06,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get those injuries \Nduring P.E. yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:38.96,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,There was this cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:49.26,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,It scratched me when I tried to help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:52.42,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,When I see a small animal,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:54.94,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help thinking of Watanuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.07,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,and I can't just leave them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:13:59.79,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to understand her,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.44,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,but everything she does \Nis actually for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:07.11,Inuboku-flashback,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's in her own world, \Nbut she's aware of what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:10.06,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.36,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.29,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,like Miketsukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:18.46,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:21.11,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I just met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.46,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't like you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:25.38,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.61,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:29.51,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,my irregular heartbeat only \Nhappens when I see him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:31.97,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,or when touches me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.32,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be what's meant by lo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:51.78,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... We just met, so it's \Ntoo early for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:53.19,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:58.32,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's that part of puberty when you can't \Nhelp but think about the opposite sex...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:02.29,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's just a natural reaction, \Nstemming from my body's changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:06.30,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it's rather late for it to happen now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:11.80,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:15.55,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I was sexually attracted to him \Nbecause he saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:28.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.57,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:55.96,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I should probably hurry home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.22,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:50.28,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there water here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:16.51,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.26,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,A nure-onna.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:26.13,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,The nure-onna, or wet woman, \Nis a creature with the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.13,0:17:28.30,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,head of a woman and the body of a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.95,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,She has long black hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:33.97,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,She is called a nure-onna because \Nher hair is always wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:37.20,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Some theories claim that she \Nis a water snake's avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:40.80,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,It's been said that she appears by water, \Nand devours people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:45.29,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,But in terms of appearance and personality, \Ntoo many different rumors exist for certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:47.88,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:51.30,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Facing danger is a man's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.84,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Women and children should stand back—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:56.18,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Watanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.20,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:06.44,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I-I won't let her run wild on my turf...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.98,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Take it easy, and stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:11.02,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to take it easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:11.95,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,You must be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:14.45,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Tanuki are on the same level as foxes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.57,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,when it comes to transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:37.51,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:40.02,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected that they'd come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:42.40,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope no one saw this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.95,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:49.22,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be gone by tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:52.58,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Probably to reappear elsewhere, \Nbut whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:55.98,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I guess I won't refuse to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:58.65,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That spell wasn't half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.43,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop petting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:12.22,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just hear something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:12.96,Default,Kid2,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:25.31,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Chiyo... Watanuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:27.48,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,You're falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:46.31,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roromiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.92,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Watanuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:59.34,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,You recognized me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:07.21,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.31,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:47.14,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:48.41,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:51.95,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,With my sixth sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:55.36,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,No, with my fifth sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.36,0:21:56.46,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:59.38,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,With my organs?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:02.50,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:08.79,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear the rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:10.23,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,I heard, I heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:11.75,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the story about the big skeleton,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:13.60,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,the tanuki, and the cosplay girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:16.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying Roromiya \Nturned into a skeleton?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:19.61,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean she was eaten \Nby a big skeleton?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.61,0:22:22.47,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,See, in the version I heard, \NRoromiya ate a tanuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:28.30,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I knew something about her was weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.90,0:22:33.29,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Whew...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.76,0:22:36.64,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like no one took a picture or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:38.13,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,That's fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:40.83,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,We'd have had to erase any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:43.42,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,You're so scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:46.59,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Young people, in the spring of youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:48.83,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,That's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.28,0:22:54.73,Default,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Roromiya did?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.73,0:22:56.88,Default,girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Really? But I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:22:59.53,Default,girl3,0000,0000,0000,,Roromiya does eat everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.53,0:23:00.85,Default,girl4,0000,0000,0000,,Though she has such a cute face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.85,0:23:05.53,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta doesn't care, so you're \Njust stressing for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:09.45,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,If you're still mad, I'll knock 'em out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.69,0:23:11.90,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Just make sure you aren't \Nknocked out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:14.02,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,What? Stop mocking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.44,0:23:15.76,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,You're good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.76,0:23:16.77,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,No, we're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.24,0:23:19.12,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you blind or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:27.97,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice when everything's lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:31.06,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bad. I won't be friendly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:32.46,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:36.81,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that, we were hanging out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.36,0:23:41.38,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,So, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:42.42,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.42,0:23:44.17,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:47.18,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,We are a man and woman, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.18,0:23:48.40,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.40,0:23:49.79,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,It's already quite late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:52.06,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, when you're together until morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.06,0:23:53.82,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't that make your heart kind of race?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:56.06,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll slice you up, and turn you into a duster.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.06,0:23:57.01,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:23:59.97,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on {\i1}Inu X Boku Secret Service{\i0}:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.97,0:24:00.91,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Their Night Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.17,0:24:05.63,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,Finally! My Ririchiyo will be \Nattacked by tentacles!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:09.01,Inuboku-next-ep-titleE5,title,0000,0000,0000,,Their Night Alone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.24,0:24:07.56,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Your nose is bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:11.96,Next timeE6,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking is about seeing \Nthe possibilities clearly.\NLook forward to next time!
